      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RITZY RUTH (2) is racing well without winning, recording three minors on end, the latest hitting the ground running with a fast early sectional but finishing in the minors again when third (24.57) over 425m at this track. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings four times from five attempts. Well-placed to take this out. SPACE KING (3) turned in a moderate run last time when fourth at this track over 425m behind Runaway Sam (24.64). The form out of last race has been strong. Has ability and can atone. FRANKLY SPEED (1) draws the rails and gets chance to find form. Last time finished last over 425m at this track beaten 11 lengths (25.10) behind Well Known in a Maiden on March 11. Key player if finds best. PARIS MASH (8) is new to this course but can play a major role.",
